summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 20W, Page 71 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (page 24-90 of the Seattle Municipal Code) to rezone certain property located on both sides of 25th Avenue West from a point one hundred feet south of West Thurman Street to Emerson Street from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of Steve Skony; C.F. \#298690).
